  <h1>The open-source library holding up your stack might have one maintainer</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jul 10, 2026</span><span>7 min read</span><span class="tag">#opensource</span><span class="tag">#supplychain</span><span class="tag">#security</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="/img/2026-07-10-open-source-single-maintainer-risk-hero.jpg" alt="Syntax-highlighted source code on a dark screen" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
